gfxeditor.shapes

Class Line

  • java.lang.Object
    • gfxeditor.Shape
      • gfxeditor.shapes.Line
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Line
extends Shape
    This shape represents a line. It internally uses a java.awt.geom.Line2D object and is automatically enumerated, starting at 1.

    • Constructor Summary

      Line(int x, int y, java.awt.Color color)
      Constructs a line with a width and height of 0 and a thickness of 1 px.
